@startuml
skinparam style strictuml
skinparam maxMessageSize 180

actor "Admin" as Admin
participant "AdminFeaturePanels.staffAccountPanel\n(View)" as View
participant "AdminController\n(Facade)" as Facade
participant "StaffAccountController" as Controller
participant "AdminService" as Service
participant "AdminStaffAccountRepository" as Repository
participant "JpaAdminDataStore" as DataStore
database "MySQL\n(BoardingHouse_DB)" as DB

Note over Admin, DB: CREATE STAFF ACCOUNT (ADMIN)

Admin -> View : 1. Nhap username/password/fullName/shift
View -> Facade : 2. createStaffAccount(...)
activate Facade

Facade -> Controller : 3. createStaffAccount(...)
activate Controller
Controller -> Service : 4. createStaffAccount(...)
activate Service
Service -> Repository : 5. createStaffAccount(...)
activate Repository
Repository -> DataStore : 6. createStaffAccount(...)
activate DataStore

DataStore -> DB : 7. Kiem tra username ton tai
activate DB
DB -->> DataStore : 8. Count
alt Username da ton tai
    DataStore -->> Repository : 9. Validation error
    Repository -->> Service : 10. Validation error
    Service -->> Controller : 11. Validation error
    Controller -->> Facade : 12. Validation error
    Facade -->> View : 13. Show duplicate message
else Username hop le
    DataStore -> DB : 14. INSERT TAI_KHOAN + INSERT NHAN_VIEN (transaction)
    DB -->> DataStore : 15. StaffAccountItem
    DataStore -->> Repository : 16. StaffAccountItem
    Repository -->> Service : 17. StaffAccountItem
    Service -->> Controller : 18. StaffAccountItem
    Controller -->> Facade : 19. Create success
    Facade -->> View : 20. Show result message
end

deactivate DB
deactivate DataStore
deactivate Repository
deactivate Service
deactivate Controller
deactivate Facade
@enduml
